    "id":"f3fd85f2-c142-424b-9a9f-eb7eac864279","type":"Full Time","url":"https://jobs.github.com/positions/f3fd85f2-c142-424b-9a9f-eb7eac864279","created_at":"Thu Mar 11 13:45:59 UTC 2021","company":"Farmy AG","company_url":"https://www.farmy.ch","location":"Barcelona","title":"Junior Android Developer (Kotlin, Java)","description":"\u003cp\u003eWe are happy to invite you to join our Android development team at the Farmy IT Department headquaters in Barcelona, Spain.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFarmy develops and runs a transparent and regional food retail platform which connects customers with farmers’ product supplies directly. When you place an order with Farmy, you get fresh food, which on the same day was collected at the farmyard, right to your doorstep or your favorite cafe – a thing, no conventional retail chain can give you. Our customers love eating healthy and fresh food, and with over 10,000 products on sale in our catalog, we do try to satisfy their appetite with every update.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur company is growing rapidly, after five successful years on the Swiss market, preparing for expansion and we’re hiring.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTasks\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaintenance and development of user and enterprise Android applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eParticipation in user experience design\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImplementation of tests\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRequirements\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWritten and spoken English\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eKotlin, Java and JVM knowledge\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with Android SDK\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFamiliarity with Android app building blocks\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave published at least one original Android app\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience working with remote data via REST and JSON.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePractical knowledge of the general mobile best practices, architecture, trends, and emerging technologies\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBenefits\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA great learning curve from day 1 on which will go beyond just Android\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOne day a week work from home (we're 100% remote for the duration of the state of emergency)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree gym abo\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAn annual budget for books and courses\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWork at a company which puts excellence and customer satisfaction at the first place\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n","how_to_apply":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://farmy.join.com/jobs/1949438-junior-android-developer-kotlin-java?pid=24ab8afa01f084c85dce\u0026amp;oid=3495185f-255e-4dc0-98e2-efc9f26b82bc\u0026amp;utm_source=github_jobs\u0026amp;utm_medium=paid\u0026amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting\u0026amp;utm_content=junior%2Bandroid%2Bdeveloper%2Bkotlin%2Bjava\"\u003ehttps://farmy.join.com/jobs/1949438-junior-android-developer-kotlin-java?pid=24ab8afa01f084c85dce\u0026amp;oid=3495185f-255e-4dc0-98e2-efc9f26b82bc\u0026amp;utm_source=github_jobs\u0026amp;utm_medium=paid\u0026amp;utm_campaign=single%2Bposting\u0026amp;utm_content=junior%2Bandroid%2Bdeveloper%2Bkotlin%2Bjava\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","company_logo":"https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZzZjIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--d98041604c97bd121c5eec213c474328b6d7c589/farmy.png"
