    "id":"c4e8d8aa-6b6b-46e2-85f3-1aafd3307919","type":"Full Time","url":"https://jobs.github.com/positions/c4e8d8aa-6b6b-46e2-85f3-1aafd3307919","created_at":"Thu Mar 11 10:49:41 UTC 2021","company":"WEBB Traders BV","company_url":"https://webbtraders.recruitee.com","location":"Amsterdam ","title":"Junior Software Engineer ","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJunior Software Engineer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompany\u003c/strong\u003e\nWEBB Traders is a fast growing global proprietary trading company and market maker active in electronic trading on leading international financial markets, driven by data and technology. We are entrepreneurial and innovative - embracing teamwork and creativity. Our headquarters is in Amsterdam city centre and is supported by a broader European and Asian presence from where the regional and US markets are traded.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAre you the all-round software engineer who will bolster our development team in Amsterdam?\u003c/strong\u003e\nWEBB Traders is looking for all-round junior engineers to join our young and dynamic R\u0026amp;D team in Amsterdam. We are responsible for the evolution of our trading solutions, tools, data processing, workflow automation and connectivity. You will be challenged and exposed to financial markets regulations, trading data, exchange/ market connectivity, reporting, risk management and quantitative/ big data analysis.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe focus on continuous improvement and technological innovation. As all-round engineer you will be a member of the development team and responsible for delivering software solutions to the various stakeholders in the company. The demands by laws and regulations on high efficient and flawless processes for countless daily trades are ever increasing. It is inevitable to work closely with traders, finance, operations, risk and compliance to deliver fast, accurate and complete solutions. Programming languages we use are C++, C# and Python. The data tools we currently use are MSSQL, MongoDB, GCP, QlikSense and others.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWould you like to work in an entrepreneurial organization and become an expert in creating solutions for our trading processes? Then we are looking for you!\u003c/strong\u003e\nYou are going to build and improve software solutions for trading, risk management, operations, finance, reporting and compliance. To keep up with the fast changing market developments, you will spend time researching new technologies and inventing new features to further our success as a global trading company. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYour work will mainly consist of:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDevelopment and optimization of software solutions for trading and all supporting processes, using C + +, Python, SQL and GCP.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply understanding and improving the numerous processes across the company.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCollaborating with your team to devise the most effective solutions.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInteracting with users to understand their objectives and improve their work through your technical ingenuity.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe opportunity to join a highly professional team in a very challenging market.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBe part of a fast growing and ambitious company.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMany opportunities to work on your personal development, such as projects, conferences, and study facilities.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInternal and external training and education in trading software, working agile, hardware and software management.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eA competitive reward package.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHealthy lunch at the office.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFree sport facility.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTravel costs reimbursement.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFun activities with colleagues on regular basis.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWho are you?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEager, curious and fast learner.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBachelor or Master degree in computer science.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e0 to 2 years experience in a software engineering role.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong computer science fundamentals.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of computer architecture, networking and databases.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience with modern C++, design patterns \u0026amp; idioms.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTeam player who thrives in an agile and fast-paced environment.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong analytical and creative problem solving skills with a ‘get it done’ mentality.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eApplication process\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eApply via \u003ca href=\"https://ltpx.nl/Kl3MgWk\"\u003ethe application form\u003c/a\u003e on our WEBB site.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePlease share with us your motivation to work with us and why you think you will fit.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave a chat via cam with us.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDo the programming challenge to show your engineering super powers.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCome and visit our office in Amsterdam for interviews and a drink.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAccept our offer!\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eAgency calls are not appreciated.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/0526deee45b4bd2c2f9ee004f93625641614d2d2/68747470733a2f2f742e6c7470782e6e6c2f747261636b2e7068703f6f7264657269643d323431353430\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","how_to_apply":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ltpx.nl/l025DGu\"\u003eClick here to apply\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","company_logo":"https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBZ1djIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--48c83e87dd054cb1f69f8ee19d870fb4151d2747/WEBB%20Traders.jpg"
