    "id":"35de12a3-33bb-494a-abee-e35217e246b7","type":"Full Time","url":"https://jobs.github.com/positions/35de12a3-33bb-494a-abee-e35217e246b7","created_at":"Wed Mar 10 09:56:56 UTC 2021","company":"SYNAOS GmbH","company_url":"https://synaos.com/","location":"Hannover","title":"(Senior) Backend Developer (m/f/d)","description":"\u003cp\u003eSYNAOS is a software start-up founded in 2018 in Hanover. We develop an ecosystem for the orchestration of intralogistics with a focus on autonomous, mobile robotics.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWe offer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFast growing, top financed start-up with highly motivated and extremely ambitious colleagues\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eChallenging tasks in developing our software platform with cutting-edge AI optimization methods and modern, scalable cloud technologies for autonomous robotics applications\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePioneering work in intralogistics for the factory and logistics centre of the future\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWith Volkswagen a DAX group as a first customer\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreative working environment with short decision-making processes (founders in the same office)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBright, newly designed offices in the heart of Hannover and good coffee from a sieving machine :)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eChoice of hardware and operating system\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnlimited employment contracts and 30 vacation days\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFlexible working hours with home office\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompetitive salaries and a development budget of 1.200 Euro per year\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYour mission\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCreation of an enterprise-capable and integrated SYNAOS ecosystem based on Java to control production and logistics\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIntegration of different technologies and systems in the backend environment\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eImplementation of agile software development (cooperation in SCRUM-teams, description of technical tasks and realization of user stories, automatic testing)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse of technologies and tools like IntelliJ, GitLab, Jira, Java, Spring Boot, Kafka, Maven, REST, Messaging, PostgreSQL, Docker, AWS\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEnthusiastic team orientation and good communication with developers, product owners and users of the software\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYour Values\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStructured working (clean code)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOpen-minded for new technologies\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCustomer focus\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTeamwork\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you bring\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAbilities\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSeveral years of experience in backend development, Java Enterprise environment or several years of professional experience in another object-oriented programming language\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProgramming and recording in English\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eExperience in developing software in a team\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePersonality\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReliability, Independence\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSolution orientation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e„Get things done“ attitude\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAttitude, values\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCommunication and capacity for teamwork\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding software as craftmanship\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStructured working method\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eContact person:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSYNAOS GmbH\nFrank Löffler\n+49 172 7617662\n\u003ca href=\"mailto:join-us@synaos.com\"\u003ejoin-us@synaos.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/bc7582304a923aaed5f57a6382fa234856019ceb/68747470733a2f2f742e676f686972696e672e636f6d2f682f32363763393035386564666439356439356164356233626539393438376661613930306635353630613739373437386432613731633838616437346161616436\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","how_to_apply":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://t.gohiring.com/h/f64e42e383577c5f71d53130e6b2273cc493ed782dc72140377c76d89b2cd0ed\"\u003eapplication form\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","company_logo":"https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdXFiIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--945d567a97e1387089a82789249c415e8735a528/SYNAOS%20GmbH.jpg"
