    "id":"bbdb156d-19e5-43da-81c5-c19a5f4223b9","type":"Full Time","url":"https://jobs.github.com/positions/bbdb156d-19e5-43da-81c5-c19a5f4223b9","created_at":"Tue Mar 09 19:10:53 UTC 2021","company":"Nanny Nina","company_url":"http://nannynina.com/","location":"Amsterdam Netherlands","title":"senior full-stack developer in Amsterdam ✨💻📱🤓🏆🥇🦸‍♂️🚲🧀","description":"\u003cp\u003eAre you one of the best in what you do? Looking for a challenging job and willing to relocate to the Netherlands (Amsterdam)? We are currently looking for a top notch Full-stack engineer with at least 2 years of working experience, preferably more.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eReq: Laravel framework: Php,Javascript, Css, HTML,Vue, (switching to either tailwind or React).\nWe have a platform including app wrap, no native app, 1 codebase\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe are looking for somebody that would like to apply for a +-32/40 hour week job. But don’t worry about your freedom. We truly cherish entrepreneurship, freedom and working independently!!\u2028\nRelocating to the Netherlands within the first year you work with us is a requirement.\nBut we love 1 person to stay with us, so you are part of the team and can improve your work, constantly learning.\u2028\u2028\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe will expand internationally this year, so we are looking for 2developers who can help us refactor code, and will build clean, well set-up features according to the UX/UI designs.\u2028\u2028We are looking for somebody nearby Amsterdam. You work 2 days at the light and spacious office in Haarlem. Preferably you work more days at the office, but minimum 2 days.\u2028\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs our full-stack develop, you are part of a diverse team. You will be working collaboratively with Digital marketeers a Product Owner, 2 great Developers and Customer Succes to develop the full user experience. With energy, ambition and an lean clean code, you guide our users to and through the most smooth flows\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u2028We are a fast growing, ambitious tech start-up, based with office in Haarlem perhaps you have seen as at the Dragons Den pitch, a show to gain investors in the Netherlands: \u003ca href=\"https://www.npostart.nl/dragons-den/19-04-2020/POW_04630483\"\u003ehttps://www.npostart.nl/dragons-den/19-04-2020/POW_04630483\u003c/a\u003e (At 36:25 for us)\u2028\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAre you or do you know someone with...\n✨ a passion for great products and code\n👀  a great eye for detail and structure\n🕵️‍♂️  a curious and ambitious mindset, eager to learn?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u2028\u2028If you are curious and would like to apply, please fill in this assignment below\u2028. We want to make sure you are a great match with the team, and the best in what you do!\u2028\nLyla ( \u003ca href=\"mailto:lylakok@nannynina.nl\"\u003elylakok@nannynina.nl\u003c/a\u003e\u2028\u2028) +31658752910\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eForm to apply\n\u003ca href=\"https://forms.gle/aMCDXfCtwiLFZN5x6\"\u003ehttps://forms.gle/aMCDXfCtwiLFZN5x6\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","how_to_apply":"\u003cp\u003eIf you would like to apply, please fill in this assignment below\u2028. We want to make sure you are a great match with the team, and the best in what you do!\u2028\nLyla ( \u003ca href=\"mailto:lylakok@nannynina.nl\"\u003elylakok@nannynina.nl\u003c/a\u003e\u2028\u2028) +31658752910\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eForm:\n\u003ca href=\"https://forms.gle/aMCDXfCtwiLFZN5x6\"\u003ehttps://forms.gle/aMCDXfCtwiLFZN5x6\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","company_logo":"https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBdFNiIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--377181418c713cf1bf8cf6d072baa9a3de444069/logo_rond_groen_RGB.png"
